el salvador has been receiving a huge slice of 
the us foreign aid program for years but now as salvadorans 
prepare to elect a new president many in congress feel us 
taxpayers have not been getting their moneys worth 
the salvadoran war still rages having claimed an estimated 
70000 lives the economy is stagnant and politicallymotivated 
