young soviet women will soon be able to discard 
their unstylish clothes and for the first time buy the same trendy 
fashions as their european and american counterparts 
three european companies are finalizing jointventures they 
believe will revolutionize soviet fashion by offering soviet women 
the western styles they can now get only from friends traveling 
abroad foreign currency stores or the black market 
the deals will put branches of britains coppernob chain and 
italys stefanel and benetton chains which all cater to the youth 
