furloughs are granted but murderers are eligible in several states 
including missouri a utah rapist won work release and was charged 
again with rape a delaware murderer was granted weekend passes 
although rules forbade it 
even inmates with clean prison records can be unpredictable 
after all they are prisoners says oklahoma prison spokesman 
jerry massie they have been convicted of crimes against society 
some states have clamped down on furloughs and early releases 
after wellpublicized crimes while others have taken similar steps 
to avoid borrowing trouble 
