communist parties committed to the democratization of the countries 
they govern 
the italian communist party broke with the soviet union in the 
1970s and has since pursued its own course which included an effort 
to rule with the christian democrats in the mid70s occhetto 
suggested saturday that that effort known as the historic 
compromise was mistaken 
the party has declined steadily in the polls over the past 
